Package: StatDesign
Title: Interactive Study Design and Sampling Platform
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Manuel", "Spínola", 
           email = "manuel.spinola@una.ac.cr",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: A Shiny-based interactive platform for study design and sampling,
    part of the StatSuite ecosystem. Includes modules for study types, sampling
    designs, design fundamentals, and an interactive assistant. Designed for
    teaching and research in ecology and biodiversity sciences.
